[27/10/2019 03:21:04] <font color="#ffffff">Hola, Vicky.</font>
[27/10/2019 03:21:04] <font color="#ffffff">Hola.</font>
[27/10/2019 03:21:06] <font color="#ffffff">¿Un sándwich de beicon?</font>
